!!! Strict
%html(xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml")
  %head
    %meta{ :content => "text/html; charset=UTF-8", "http-equiv".intern => "Content-Type"}

    %style
      blockquote { padding-left: 10px; border-left: 1px solid #666; }
  %body
    %p
      Hi #{@user.name},

    - if @point    
      %p
        #{@comment.user.name} commented on a #{@point.is_pro ? 'pro' : 'con'} point for "#{@point.proposal.title}" that you also commented on. The point states that "#{@point.nutshell}". The comment says:

      %blockquote
        #{@comment.body}

      %p
        Respond at
        = succeed '.' do
          = proposal_point_url(@point.proposal.long_id, @point)

    - elsif @position
      %p
        #{@comment.user.name} also commented on #{@position.user.name}'s review.
      %p 
        Go 
        %a{ :href => "#{proposal_url(@position.proposal)}" }
          here
        to read and respond. 

    %p
      Thanks!

    %p 
      p.s. We apologize if the above comment is offensive. We will review any comment deemed offensive (such as containing a personal attack), and block the offending commenter if appropriate. 

    %hr

    %p
      To unsubscribe to these messages, visit the link above, and modify your review by deselecting the checkbox near the bottom of the page.   